ygData.msgSnippet: Heh well if you head to Solusk B and auction there you might be lucky and get one for 10pp or so. Usually I find myself and my partners just selling to vendors
ygData.messageBody:
Heh well if you head to Solusk B and auction there you might be lucky and
get one for 10pp or so. Usually I find myself and my partners just selling
to vendors so you may get lucky.

Naeeldar
